name: VEG (CodeFortress)
description:
HEY, In this game you are a vegetable buyer... But recently some of the sellers has started selling fake vegetables. So you have to guess which food is real and which one isn't... You are given some specific vegetables to buy... but if you pick a fake vegetable. The you will lose. Good LUCK! ;) CREDITS, programming: Code Fortress Drawings: BRACKEYS
